<p>Before, we used this syntax to query for a <code>Programmer</code> by its nickname.
But it also has a special "last" keyword, which queries for the last record
in the table. Again, this is <em>me</em> adding special things to <em>my</em> Behat project.
Which is really handy for testing the API.</p>
