<h2 id="creating-the-get-endpoint">Creating the GET Endpoint <a class="headerlink" href="get-one-battle#creating-the-get-endpoint" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>Let's get this working! In <code>BattleController</code>, add a new GET endpoint for
<code>/api/battles/{id}</code> and change the method to <code>showAction</code>. Because
we have a <code>{id}</code> in the path, the <code>showAction</code> will have an <code>$id</code>
argument.</p>
