<p>Wow, and it already passes. This is getting <em>really really</em> easy, which is
why we put in all the work before this.</p>
<h2 id="don-t-forget-to-fix-the-location-header">Don't Forget to Fix the Location Header <a class="headerlink" href="get-one-battle#don-t-forget-to-fix-the-location-header" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>Now that we have a proper <code>showAction</code>, we can go back and fix the "todo"
in the header. First, we'll need to give the route an internal name - <code>api_battle_show</code>:</p>
